{"tid":1717300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11.13土瓜灣被捕 麻煩認人","createTime":"2019-11-13T14:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T20:07:32.000Z","uid":5395,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"95685c835965940cced3681e47054b6904dfa8a3","tid":1717300,"uid":5395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:40:58.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣噚晚先開齋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇乜人知有行動同冇記者跟進<br />\n麻煩幫幫手認人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n土瓜灣遊樂場 1男1女<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KB7HXjN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKB7HXjN.jpg&h=d54d665c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/abcdellen1992/videos/10216016893123665/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fabcdellen1992%2Fvideos%2F10216016893123665%2F&d=jGmFyvXa%2BxCeqK61Wy4ey0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=8a225e3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/abcdellen1992/videos/10216016893123665/</a><br />\n<br />\n牛棚公廁附近(變電站) 2男<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xz15U6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXz15U6U.jpg&h=0826ef12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJenXmg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJenXmg.jpg&h=2bf07a00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇記者得街坊影所以好難睇<br />\n冇正面嘅認吓髮型同有冇土瓜灣朋友失蹤咗<br />\n暫時得咁多，有嘅下面再update"},{"pid":"d1725c60e51d88fed54fc0559e5ff5ff2172b8d1","tid":1717300,"uid":5395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:41:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6de692de9d405b14a29313ef1dbb33a489af994","tid":1717300,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fcac841635d9706ebcf4190cec8e2e0bda524fdb","tid":1717300,"u